query: SELECT c.tenantId, COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as cash_count, COUNT(DISTINCT r.id) as receivables_count, COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as payables_count FROM cash_flow c LEFT JOIN receivables r ON c.tenantId = r.tenantId LEFT JOIN payables p ON c.tenantId = p.tenantId GROUP BY c.tenantId ORDER BY cash_count DESC LIMIT 1;
